{"tid":1294662,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"失眠真係慘過食屎","createTime":"2019-07-07T22:11:21.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-07T22:40:08.000Z","uid":246648,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"e1b49ce178a0bf4e0d6f3ad8ec6653d523b7e23e","tid":1294662,"uid":246648,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T22:11:21.000Z","msg":"訓教係咩黎？人類點解可以訓著？<br />\n<br />\n合埋眼咪即係望住塊眼皮，咁就叫訓著？<br />\n<br />\n無訓幾耐先叫失眠？<br />\n<br />\n咩叫唔好諗野？諗住唔好諗野咪又係諗緊野，你班晚晚訓得著既人剩係識叫人唔好諗野，呢句野根本難聽過粗口，累到極點自然會訓著？果啲唔係叫訓教，果啲叫昏迷啊仆街，咁可以點啊？無架啦，諗野又唔係病黎無得醫<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我睇唔透<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n其實我只係想問下有無邊隻安眠藥好用<br />\n<br />\nthx<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/oPPs1av.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FoPPs1av.jpg&h=7bd0327e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"7a77c11d57f619fe484c65c7032fad57e9d78b4d","tid":1294662,"uid":8500,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T22:11:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"de48e783123367195fa4a6cacba7738e84ce958b","tid":1294662,"uid":59838,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T22:12:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f30c2a8a53bb77ace1d40d4764c67be5a45624a3","tid":1294662,"uid":2531,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T22:14:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />訓唔着lm"},{"pid":"32fe6b4241238cb2e7691abda4a4eeb6713f7ac8","tid":1294662,"uid":118125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T22:14:58.000Z","msg":"我都訓唔著，睇黑警惡行睇左幾個鐘<img src=\"/asset